    <p>Our advanced machine learning analysis has revealed fascinating patterns in powder probability across European ski destinations. A "powder day" in our analysis is defined as any day with 10cm or more of fresh snow - the threshold that turns a good ski day into an unforgettable one. In table below you can see resorts with highest probability of powder day in each month. Overall La Clusaz-Manigod has the highest powder day probability</p>
    
